  "title": "Order Processing Team Lead (PERM) - Up to $3K #HKH",
  "description": "<ul><li>The primary purpose of this role is to oversee the daily operations of our warehouse including incoming, put away, pick/pack, supervising staff, documentation and ensuring a safe and efficient workflow.</li><li>Leading warehouse assistants in daily operations.</li><li>Ensure proper storage of goods and maintain good housekeeping.</li><li>Perform cycle count & investigate inventory discrepancies.</li><li>Support warehouse tasks including SAP system transactions.</li><li>Coordinate and collaborate within the team and with other departments. </li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, WMS/SAP experience is an added advantage. </li><li>Must be willing to work overtime – alternate weekdays and on alternate Saturdays </li></ul><p>West Area </p><p>Up to $3K </p><p>Scientific industry </p><p></p><p><em>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to</em><em><strong> kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em></p><p><em>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338)</em></p><p><em>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</em></p>",
